# Demo: taskwing knowledge decision
# Browse architectural decisions

Require taskwing

Output demos/knowledge-decision.gif
Output demos/knowledge-decision.mp4

Set Shell "zsh"
Set FontSize 16
Set Width 1200
Set Height 900
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set Padding 20
Set TypingSpeed 50ms
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set WindowBarSize 40
Set Framerate 24
Set PlaybackSpeed 1
Set LoopOffset 0%

Sleep 1s

Type@60ms "taskwing knowledge decision"
Enter
Sleep 6s

Sleep 3s
